
Persona - Spring Boot Application
====================================


#### Requirements
1. Java 8
2. Tomcat 8

apache-maven-4.0.0

## Accessing Application
Based on the properties specified to start application, Persona can be accessed at:


##get All Personas
http://localhost:8080/persona/findAll



##Save Persona
Post:

http://localhost:8080/persona/save

{	
    "name": "Rakesh",
    "lastName": "aa",
    "address": "bb",
    "phoneNumber": 123,
    "hairColorEnum": "YELLOW"
}



##edit by id
GET

http://localhost:8080/persona/edit/1





##delete by id
GET

http://localhost:8080/persona/delete/4




